08:42.688 --> 08:45.900
your son has developmental issues
on the spectrum.

08:45.984 --> 08:47.986
Everybody's different, doc.

08:48.069 --> 08:50.071
I don't need a test
to know he's perfectly fine.

08:53.241 --> 08:54.241
We all set?

09:28.651 --> 09:30.653
<i>How low am I on the totem pole</i>

09:30.737 --> 09:34.574
to be covering a handicapped librarian
directing a passion play?

09:35.283 --> 09:36.159
That's nice.

09:36.242 --> 09:38.411
