you know?

09:38.953 --> 09:42.040
School raises $5,000
to help for medical expenses.

09:42.415 --> 09:43.666
It's, like, super sweet.

09:43.750 --> 09:45.418
Yeah, it's sweet.

09:46.753 --> 09:47.962
Always sweet...

09:48.546 --> 09:49.631
for Beth Flowers.

09:52.801 --> 09:54.177
It's definitely my name.

09:54.928 --> 09:56.096
I gotta change my name.

09:56.387 --> 10:00.016
No. Beth Flowers is, like,
a super catchy news name.

10:01.392 --> 10:04.521
