That weatherman in L.A.?

10:05.605 --> 10:06.856
He's not even from Dallas.

10:06.940 --> 10:08.399
No. Small market.

10:09.317 --> 10:11.778
Why can't I cover something
with national appeal?

10:12.237 --> 10:14.614
Like, I don't know...

10:15.448 --> 10:16.699
a cult, or...

10:18.409 --> 10:20.161
a government sex scandal?

10:20.245 --> 10:21.245
Yeah.

10:21.996 --> 10:25.250
- Let's hope something like that happens.
- Oh, God. I gotta pee.

10:29.003 --> 10:30.505
Okay.

10:32.549 --> 10:34.759
Have you decided
what you're gonna name that thing?

10:34.843 --> 10:36.302
Is Heather still in the running?

10:36.886 --> 10:38.721
