10:40.056 --> 10:42.308
Liza or Megan. I don't know.

10:42.392 --> 10:44.519
Suzy's cute. I like Suzy with a Z.

10:44.602 --> 10:47.856
Love Suzy. I knew a stripper
in Cincinnati named Suzy, right?

10:47.939 --> 10:49.232
She did this move, right?

10:49.315 --> 10:51.359
Where she gripped the pole
with both legs.

10:51.442 --> 10:54.737
She was twerking at the top of the pole
and she just dropped down.

10:54.863 --> 10:57.615
We thought she had to go to the hospital,
but she was fine.

10:57.740 --> 11:00.201
- That's what she does every night.
- Don't look!

11:00.285 --> 11:02.120
I'm not looking. I'm talking to you.

11:06.583 --> 11:08.293
You all save room for cake?

11:08.626 --> 11:10.503
No. No, thank you. Not today.

11:12.547 --> 11:13.882
Dessert's a treat, babe.

11:14.424 --> 11:15.967
All right. Take your time.

11:16.050 --> 11:18.636
You know, Momma can't afford dessert
at every meal.

11:19.137 --> 11:21.472
And you don't need any more sugar.

11:23.016 --> 11:25.226
- Everything good?
- Yes, ma'am. Very good.

11:25.727 --> 11:27.687
You don't have to lie.

11:28.980 --> 11:32.567
Is there a grocery store close
or anywhere I can buy a couple things?

11:32.650 --> 11:34.319
Next door's got about everything.

11:35.612 --> 11:37.030
How much is this cake here?

11:37.405 --> 11:39.616
$3.95. Worth every penny.

11:40.825 --> 11:43.745
- Can you send a piece to the little man?
- Aw!

11:51.419 --> 11:53.296
No, we said we weren't going to get
any cake.

11:53.379 --> 11:54.839
It's that gentleman right there.

11:55.632 --> 11:56.716
He bought it for you.

12:06.809 --> 12:08.061
There he is, right there.

12:09.479 --> 12:10.688
Look at that.

12:10.772 --> 12:12.857
Got a gallon of Drano right there.

12:12.941 --> 12:14.984
That's a main ingredient in meth.

12:15.485 --> 12:18.196
He's paying cash.
He's got fraudulent credit cards.

12:18.279 --> 12:21.908
Knows dick about his car. Look, Billy,
this ain't brain science here.

12:22.492 --> 12:23.952
It's probable cause.

12:24.994 --> 12:28.456
And that's probably
'cause he's likely up to no good.

12:28.915 --> 12:30.083
Oh, that's for certain.

12:35.046 --> 12:36.047
Mm!

12:38.049 --> 12:40.051
Oh, look at that.

12:42.011 --> 12:43.011
Oh.

12:43.846 --> 12:45.807
Dental hygienist.

12:45.890 --> 12:46.891
We're home.

12:46.975 --> 12:48.476
Yes, you are.

12:48.893 --> 12:51.479
Unless you're my date
and didn't knock.

12:51.813 --> 12:53.564
Where are you? Come here!

12:53.648 --> 12:56.109
What are you so happy about today?

12:57.485 --> 12:58.528
Look at that.

12:59.320 --> 13:00.405
You finished it.

13:01.614 --> 13:04.742
- ♪ <i>The itsy-bitsy spider... ♪</i>
- Are you going out again tonight?

13:05.159 --> 13:08.079
Well,
I can't find a man sitting in here.

13:08.496 --> 13:10.623
Tried that already. It only worked once.

13:11.416 --> 13:14.294
You didn't like that cable guy, did ya?

13:14.752 --> 13:16.838
<i>"He sprang to his sleigh,</i>

13:16.921 --> 13:19.590
to his team gave a whistle,

13:19.841 --> 13:23.594
and away they all flew
like the down on a thistle.

13:23.928 --> 13:27.724
But I heard him exclaim,
ere he drove out of sight,

13:28.141 --> 13:32.312
'Happy Christmas to all,
and to all a good night.'"

13:36.691 --> 13:38.276
No, buddy, it's your turn.

13:38.359 --> 13:41.070
You wanna be a big boy,
you gotta read it all by yourself.

13:48.745 --> 13:51.247
I have to work a couple hours,
so I'll be back by eight.

13:51.331 --> 13:53.583
Dental hygienist is taking me bowling!

13:55.001 --> 13:57.003
He's anxious to meet the Jewels.

13:57.128 --> 13:59.130
Come on, Ma. I don't ask for much.

13:59.339 --> 14:01.466
Seth's reading. He's not gonna bug you.

14:01.549 --> 14:04.177
Oh, my God, this is short.

14:04.427 --> 14:06.429
Well, I guess we can just hang out here.

14:07.472 --> 14:10.183
Forget it. I'll be back in time
for you to go out.

14:10.266 --> 14:12.268
You got a sexy bowling shirt or something?

14:12.352 --> 14:15.271
- They don't make sexy bowling shirts.
- Well, they should.

14:15.605 --> 14:17.565
Need to spice up that sport.

14:53.267 --> 14:54.267
Excuse me.

14:56.229 --> 14:57.438
Excuse me.

15:04.529 --> 15:06.030
- Excuse me.
- God!

15:06.114 --> 15:09.075
- You scared the crap outta me!
- Sorry. I didn't mean to...

15:09.158 --> 15:11.828
Well, you did.
The hell are you standing over me for?

15:11.911 --> 15:14.591
- I was trying to get something to drink...
- You hover over people?

15:14.664 --> 15:15.832
Scare the shit outta them?

15:15.915 --> 15:17.625
Take it easy, all right? I'm sorry.

15:17.708 --> 15:18.835
I'm sorry.

15:19.627 --> 15:20.627
What do you want?

15:21.838 --> 15:24.090
I'll take the tequila there.

15:24.382 --> 15:25.382
Please.

15:27.343 --> 15:28.928
It's $26.50.

15:31.431 --> 15:33.141
What were you reading?

15:33.933 --> 15:34.933
I'm studying.

15:34.976 --> 15:36.060
Oh, what for?

15:36.936 --> 15:38.020
What, are you a cop?

15:38.104 --> 15:40.815
Do I look like one?

15:44.068 --> 15:46.028
I go to college in Baxter twice a week.

15:46.946 --> 15:48.906
At night, for your information.

15:49.574 --> 15:51.200
Hmm. What are you studying?

15:51.951 --> 15:54.787
Developmental biology.
Do you want to know my sign, too?

16:02.587 --> 16:04.005
Thanks for the cake.

16:05.923 --> 16:08.509
Yeah. You're welcome.

16:09.177 --> 16:10.177
Why'd you do that?

16:10.928 --> 16:12.889
I was just trying to be nice.

16:13.389 --> 16:15.391
Yeah? For what?

16:18.227 --> 16:20.480
I just think a kid should have
a piece of cake.

16:23.107 --> 16:24.107
Thanks.

16:24.775 --> 16:25.775
You're welcome.

17:07.527 --> 17:08.527
Yeah, what?

17:09.862 --> 17:11.571
I'm looking for a Mr. Roth?

17:11.696 --> 17:14.700
- A Mr. Michael Roth?
- No Michael fucker here now.

17:15.159 --> 17:16.786
Get the hell away from my door.

17:17.161 --> 17:18.954
Do you know of a Michael Roth?

17:20.164 --> 17:22.625
What the fuck is the matter with you?

17:24.544 --> 17:27.964
He used to live here. I was wondering
if you had any information about him,

17:28.047 --> 17:31.676
- or knew anyone who did, or anything...
- No, no, and no.

17:31.759 --> 17:33.052
Now, fuck off.

17:33.511 --> 17:35.888
- Hold on a second...
- You wanna break those fingers?

17:35.972 --> 17:38.724
- I can do that.
- I found this letter. It's 15 years old,

17:38.808 --> 17:40.601
but that's the return address.

17:43.771 --> 17:45.398
What are you, stupid?

17:45.815 --> 17:48.693
Nobody lives in this shit factory
for 15 years.

17:51.195 --> 17:53.489
All right. I'm sorry to disturb you.

17:53.948 --> 17:57.577
Eh. You took a shot, you know?
You can cross it off your list.

18:10.506 --> 18:12.216
Hey, man. Listen.

18:12.800 --> 18:16.012
There was a guy in here before me.
A veteran type.

18:16.804 --> 18:19.098
I'll tell you all about him
if you buy me a drink.

18:21.142 --> 18:22.685
Come on! Tell you what,

18:22.768 --> 18:26.063
if it wasn't him, we got nothing
to talk about, it cost you a beer.

18:26.147 --> 18:28.149
- I'm good, man.
- It's Christmas.

18:28.608 --> 18:31.360
Ho, ho, ho. Who's gonna know?

18:37.867 --> 18:39.619
Hey. You mind?

18:40.244 --> 18:42.496
- Help yourself.
- All right.

18:42.580 --> 18:44.999
Praise the Lord. He always provides.

18:49.378 --> 18:52.673
Hey, nice ride. What is it, a '71?

18:53.883 --> 18:57.303
That's the year I found
our Lord and Savior Jesus Christ,

18:57.386 --> 18:59.430
and the honorable Jack Daniels.

18:59.513 --> 19:00.973
Jack's still with me.

19:01.849 --> 19:03.225
So, what's your name?

19:04.226 --> 19:06.771
Bukowski. My friends call me Charles.

19:07.855 --> 19:10.149
- Original.
- That's me, one of a kind.

19:12.526 --> 19:15.154
Since we're getting friendly,
what do they call you?

19:15.363 --> 19:16.363
Eric.

19:18.574 --> 19:19.742
Where are we going?

19:20.993 --> 19:25.081
While I get my bearings,
you drive, I'll point.

19:46.727 --> 19:48.187
Hey, uh, Tammy.

19:48.354 --> 19:49.480
Two Pabst.

19:49.563 --> 19:51.440
Actually, I'll take a Heineken.

19:51.649 --> 19:53.025
The Pabst are for me.

19:53.109 --> 19:55.486
You order whatever you want.
You're paying.

19:55.569 --> 19:57.029
Uh, Heineken, please.

19:57.113 --> 19:59.156
- You got it, darling.
- Oh, man.

19:59.240 --> 20:01.909
Um... you got any quarters?

20:02.535 --> 20:04.120
- For what?
- The jukebox.

20:05.496 --> 20:07.832
Look, I don't have time for this.
Are we gonna talk?

20:07.915 --> 20:09.375
It's about ambiance.

20:09.458 --> 20:12.128
It's a fucking holiday.
Show a little class.

20:17.091 --> 20:18.259
Ah.

20:18.884 --> 20:19.719
Here you go.

20:19.802 --> 20:21.470
<i>- Gracias.
- Por nada.</i>

20:21.595 --> 20:23.264
- And <i>gracias. </i> Ah.
- Enjoy.

20:23.806 --> 20:26.100
Oh, man. All righty.

20:38.028 --> 20:41.115
