Watch where you're going,
you drunk fucker!

20:48.706 --> 20:49.706
Drunk fucker?

20:49.749 --> 20:50.791
- Shit.
- Watch it!

20:50.875 --> 20:52.793
Hey! Settle down!

20:52.877 --> 20:55.004
- Get off me!
- Take it easy. He's drunk.

20:55.087 --> 20:57.089
